Embedded_Microprocessor_System_Design_using_FPGAs  2. edition

Here is a brief overview of the new 2/e CD files and the related book chapters.
============================================================
* Linux (Chapter 12)
  -- shell scripts used in the chapter 
  -- directory gpio for the PETALINUX gpio-demo
  -- directory ko for the Kernel demo
  -- directory sql for the MySQL demo

* Python (Chapter 13)
  -- demo programs used in the chapter
  -- shell script libpyl.sh to install popular embedded system libs
  -- shell script runPYall.sh to run all demos

* JavaScript  (Chapter 14)
  -- HTML, CSS, and JS demos used in the chapter
  -- Test programs used for Table 14.3 and 14.4
  -- ES language check scripts ESnode.sh
  -- Node language support check script NodeDemo.sh

* Java (Chapter 15)
  -- Java demos used in the chapter (check run with SEprog.sh)
  -- Test programs used for Table 15.2 and 15.3
  -- SE language support feature check SEfeature.sh
  -- SE language support check script SEall.sh

* Videos (All Chapters)
  -- 46 videos (21 new) from all chapters

===========================================================
See Embedded_Microprocessor_System_Design_using_FPGAs  1. edition
directory for HDL files, board ZIP files.
See the util directory for compiler, font, HDL etc. utilies.
